pageContext.content: Phoenix based Kirkwood Dellinger, also known simply as KD, was formed in September of 06′ by Elmo Kirkwood and Brian Dellinger. Known for their wild stage shows with band members switching off instruments in nearly every song, the band has music in their bloodline as Elmo Kirkwood is also the son and nephew of Curt and Cris Kirkwood of the Meat Puppets.
